description:
BEYOND the DARKNESS meets MONSTERS Or MYTHS: Cracking Cryptid Conspiracies with Scott Marlowe.

We look into REALITY TV and the Hype or Hoax of the most recent years of Cryptid TV programming. Scott enlightens us to some ACTUAL findings and science regarding these mysteries.

Find his books here: www.Amazon.com/shop/darknessradio
